## Coventry-class Royal Navy frigate

For other vessels bearing the name [HMS Liverpool](/HMS_Liverpool), consult the relevant disambiguation page.

### Ship plan of Liverpool

The schematics offer a glimpse into the design of the [HMS Liverpool](/HMS_Liverpool), a vessel that, for all its naval significance, ultimately met a rather ignominious end. It’s a testament to the era’s shipbuilding, a blend of calculated design and the inherent risks of maritime endeavor. One can almost feel the creak of the timber, the salt spray on the decks, just by observing these lines.

### History

