*   **Name:** HMS Liverpool
*   **Ordered:** 3 September 1756
*   **Builder:** John Gorill & William Pownall, [Liverpool](/Liverpool)
*   **Laid down:** 1 October 1756
*   **Launched:** 10 February 1758
*   **Commissioned:** February 1758
*   **Fate:** Wrecked 1778

